    player docks at a starbase.
         You may start recieving propaganda  messages  from  the  Klingon
    commander if he feels he has you in a tight situation.

    Entering Commands:

         Commands are entered as  numbers  (Terminated  by  pressing  the
    return  key)  in  response to the question "Command?".  Some commands
    may require additional information.  Those that do will ask  for  the
    additional information.  A response of -1 to any question will result
    in the command being canceled.

